    "causal_summary": "Track the end-to-end embedder and reranker program across the 013 umbrella. The current production posture is no longer the original Jina/mxbai scaffold: mk-spec-memory defaults to the Nomic/CodeRankEmbed local bi-encoder path through the Ollama -> hf-local Nomic cascade, CocoIndex defaults to `sbert/nomic-ai/CodeRankEmbed` for code embeddings, and CocoIndex reranks through `Qwen/Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B` via the shared sidecar by default.",
